{"tid":1573090,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[非屌人] FA可以救人 但係有一個條件","createTime":"2019-09-16T01:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T02:27:23.000Z","uid":282910,"like":32,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f45e96bfcc5d583d9ddaf2ede1db8a7cd5a801ac","tid":1573090,"uid":282910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:04:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>基於人道理由 有手足想救藍絲 我覺得ok（雖然我份人比較功利 一定唔救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</strong><br />\n<br />\n但可唔可以等藍絲完全失去戰鬥能力 / 即時活動能力 先救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時個藍絲重郁到 只係頭流血 （需知黃絲比較有仁愛 暫未開發關節技)<br />\n你咁快幫佢急救 真係可能十分鐘後佢又拎刀斬手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議係<br />\n藍絲暈左 / 斷手斷腳 / 明顯無傷害性 -&gt; 可以救<br />\n藍絲重郁得 -&gt; 唔好救 因為仍然戰鬥中 你打仗都唔會打到一半 (敵人重揸住支槍) 走去幫敵人急救啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打完先救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持 -&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對 -&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5874281493e1bd10f31996da269629ea15b2150b","tid":1573090,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:09:42.000Z","msg":"我以為你想講學左綱手個招百豪之術先可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, Sor 幫你推"},{"pid":"8f7a6aca82d7019bf41ca0d7b512222eee4168ed","tid":1573090,"uid":282910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5874281493e1bd10f31996da269629ea15b2150b","tid":1573090,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:09:42.000Z","msg":"我以為你想講學左綱手個招百豪之術先可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, Sor 幫你推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:15:54.000Z","msg":"幫手推 P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"f4d5f8357f0f4723ff21583465121b0f46e9d3f4","tid":1573090,"uid":313318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:16:41.000Z","msg":"P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86344817b55e904b1029a4aa79fd34e89ae3e6b4","tid":1573090,"uid":75461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"班藍絲無腦，佢仲有戰鬥力嗰時救佢隨時比佢打返轉頭。記唔記得之前太子站有個義士救個藍絲啊叔，反而比個藍絲啊叔幫返黑警拉個義士。記住，幫蠍子🦂️過河，隨時會被殺。"},{"pid":"e17043a67113b3c5c4d958349c722e880236d362","tid":1573090,"uid":87755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"同意 佢仲有戰鬥力行動力個陣唔洗救<br />\n救完佢又上戰場害手足"},{"pid":"8d75c9a526478b1cbf9a98995661a911fc299524","tid":1573090,"uid":51623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"考CPR第一樣就係要等現場環境安全先<br />\n<br />\n即係等到無人再跌親嗰陣先去救"},{"pid":"b462cd684ff37f99215fedbc35674f9cfc25883d","tid":1573090,"uid":916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:34:02.000Z","msg":"救藍屍果時就算手腳冇事都照包住手/腳/頸<br />\n然後同佢講你跌落地果時懷疑d骨錯左位, 一郁就會斷骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31899f259255dc7dd55b6809abd6ed14e55f107","tid":1573090,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:34:44.000Z","msg":"照救<br />\n但可能心急得濟唔小心大大力㩒咗落個傷口度<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d50f15664e0d2047d65f70dea1a1aa73e06102f","tid":1573090,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b462cd684ff37f99215fedbc35674f9cfc25883d","tid":1573090,"uid":916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:34:02.000Z","msg":"救藍屍果時就算手腳冇事都照包住手/腳/頸<br />\n然後同佢講你跌落地果時懷疑d骨錯左位, 一郁就會斷骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:37:04.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f4c1d45bcbfdfc6fdb984a2207baccbc811062","tid":1573090,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:38:42.000Z","msg":"FA 其實冇得簡， 救護工作係一定唔理邊邊都要救。<br />\n如果佢選擇性黎救，一定比狗趕絕<br />\n你可以見到藍絲唔叫FA, 但佢見到佢都冇得簡，一定要救。"},{"pid":"d08b3f0c9e4ec8e2219fc5ad489c8c0b21cbcc81","tid":1573090,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"First aid 救人都要接受你d 條件<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎喇</span><br />\n<br />\n各有各做，嚴格黎講First aid唔係你手足<br />\n佢地盡佢地專業救人，咁都唔得？"},{"pid":"753a0c9f247918e2e0ae562b8d6c4efdaeedb7b1","tid":1573090,"uid":294844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d08b3f0c9e4ec8e2219fc5ad489c8c0b21cbcc81","tid":1573090,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"First aid 救人都要接受你d 條件<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎喇</span><br />\n<br />\n各有各做，嚴格黎講First aid唔係你手足<br />\n佢地盡佢地專業救人，咁都唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"啱，個救護員係藍絲既話咁手足就仆街等死喇"},{"pid":"4c86b7eab7a2c8252495430baa2da0c99381bb41","tid":1573090,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:46:39.000Z","msg":"反對<br />\n藍絲必須死<br />\n救都唔應該救"},{"pid":"889a10d4718602fc542f5c28df45a57a5180165e","tid":1573090,"uid":282910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d08b3f0c9e4ec8e2219fc5ad489c8c0b21cbcc81","tid":1573090,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"First aid 救人都要接受你d 條件<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎喇</span><br />\n<br />\n各有各做，嚴格黎講First aid唔係你手足<br />\n佢地盡佢地專業救人，咁都唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"你諗下 假設係外國<br />\n有人打劫緊銀行 期間俾警察射左一槍 可能只係擦傷 或者無中要害<br />\n總之重有危險性啦<br />\n啲救護會唔會專業地衝上前幫個賊急救先&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係等個賊被制伏左，係救護車 / 醫院入面先開始救架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83557b84764fac89d8c754c3bb12ff0a0b0e9be","tid":1573090,"uid":282910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c86b7eab7a2c8252495430baa2da0c99381bb41","tid":1573090,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:46:39.000Z","msg":"反對<br />\n藍絲必須死<br />\n救都唔應該救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:27:23.000Z","msg":"我都想呀大佬"}]}